      "side": 1,
      "message": "A lot of these return a zx_status_t that you should at least be ZX_CHECKing or ASSERT_NEing, but you’ve only ZX_CHECKed the launchpad_go().\n\n(Learnin’ based on my exploratory work at https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/crashpad/crashpad/+/820532/4/test/fuchsia/run_and_log.cc#226, which isn’t ready for anything yet.)",
      "revId": "2cf28382bc56edde002ebb1dc898e25374647a89",
