    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "e8432d68_b4ae9c0e",
        "filename": "test/multiprocess_exec_fuchsia.cc",
        "patchSetId": 14
      },
      "lineNbr": 135,
      "author": {
        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-01-17T21:43:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Do you want to launchpad_clone() anything here?\n\nThe only thing you definitely don’t want is LP_CLONE_FDIO_ALL.\n\nI don’t know how LP_CLONE_FDIO_STDIO behaves in conjunction with launchpad_add_pipe() that replaces stdin and stdout. It might be fine and would be an easy way to bring stderr into the child. Otherwise, please arrange to bring stderr to the child yourself, otherwise we’ll lose children’s useful diagnostics.\n\nYou definitely do want LP_CLONE_ENVIRON, almost certainly want LP_CLONE_FDIO_NAMESPACE, and based on my understanding, probably want LP_CLONE_DEFAULT_JOB too.",
      "revId": "2cf28382bc56edde002ebb1dc898e25374647a89",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
    },
